episodes.title: ‘Impostor, deceiver’: Quiboloy alleged victim says ‘fear consumed me’
episodes.description:
Teresita Valdehueza, a former follower of doomsday preacher Apollo Quiboloy, explained that other women had experienced the same, claiming it was God's way for them to 'surrender their body, soul, and spirit'.

Full story: https://www.rappler.com/philippines/quiboloy-alleged-sexual-victim-says-fear-consumed-me/

episodes.title: Police sweep Davao compound in another large-scale manhunt for Quiboloy
episodes.description:
Hundreds of police officers launched another search for fugitive doomsday preacher Apollo Quiboloy in the 30-hectare property of the Kingdom of Jesus Christ (KOJC) in Davao City on Saturday morning, August 24.

Full story: https://www.rappler.com/philippines/mindanao/cops-sweep-davao-compound-large-scale-manhunt-apollo-quiboloy-august-24-2024/
